metadata.title: SeekSense
metadata.description:
Robotic Semantic Navigation & Asset Search – Short Survey
This 3–4 minute survey is for people who work with mobile robots in indoor environments (warehouses, hospitals, labs, campuses, etc.).
We’re researching how teams currently handle “find this trolley/cart/asset” tasks and whether training-free semantic navigation (robots that can search by description, not just waypoints) would be useful.
Your responses will be aggregated and anonymised. With your permission, we may use the results as part of our market research evidence. We will not share your details with third parties or use them for marketing without your consent.
